
HOW TO INSTALL THE SAIM MODULE:
===============================

- Copy this folder to the addons folder of your openerp instance
- Restart the service with --update=saim
- Install the module via web interface
- Before using the module:
 * Define the variables in the file settings.py according to your deployment
 * Execute the command 'python importar_estados.py' and wait for it to finish 

Now you will have the module working properly with all the geographic information that is needed.
